OL,3,CPolice bill for investigation into SNP
OL,4,Cfinances tops #2m
OL,6,FPolice Scotland has spent more than #2
OL,7,Fmillion on the investigation into the
OL,8,FSNP's finances.
OL,10,FThe bill for Operation Branchform
OL,11,Fstood at #2,173,089 as of April 30,
OL,12,Fthe force said in response to a
OL,13,Ffreedom of information request.
OL,15,FThe probe was launched in 2021 to
OL,16,Finvestigate the SNP's funding and
OL,17,Ffinances and has involved several high-
OL,18,Fprofile arrests.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/7
