OL,3,CPolice bill for investigation into SNP
OL,4,Cfinances tops #2m
OL,6,FPeter Murrell, the ex-husband of
OL,7,Fformer first minister Nicola Sturgeon,
OL,8,Fhas been charged with allegedly
OL,9,Fembezzling nearly #460,000 from the
OL,10,Fparty.
OL,12,FThe former SNP chief executive is set
OL,13,Fto appear in court on Monday.
OL,15,FPolice Scotland said #100,498 has been
OL,16,Fspent on overtime in the five years
OL,17,Fsince the investigation began. The
OL,18,Fforce also said the #2 million figure
OL,19,Fdoes not include pension contributions.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
