PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1779584596
OL,3,CPolice bill for investigation into SNP
OL,4,Cfinances tops #2m
OL,6,FThe costs do not cover those accrued
OL,7,Fby the Crown Office.
OL,9,FScottish Labour said the probe only
OL,10,Fadds to the financial pressures facing
OL,11,Fthe country's national police force.
OL,13,FPauline McNeill, the party's justice
OL,14,Fspokeswoman, said: "Given the dire
OL,15,Fstate of the country's finances as a
OL,16,Fresult of SNP incompetence, the SNP
OL,17,Fmust urgently clarify whether they
OL,18,Fintend to make any cuts to Police
OL,19,FScotland budgets in the years ahead.
OL,26,@vD@TOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
