OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1779584596
OL,3,CPolice bill for investigation into SNP
OL,4,Cfinances tops #2m
OL,6,F"It cannot be the case that financial
OL,7,Fpressures are further heaped on the
OL,8,Fservice as a result of the negligence
OL,9,Fof ministers, or because money has had
OL,10,Fto be spent investigating allegations
OL,11,Fof SNP fraud.
OL,13,F"Taxpayers should not have to foot the
OL,14,Fbill due to the actions of senior SNP
OL,15,Ffigures, with our communities less
OL,16,Fsafe due to any potential decline in
OL,17,Fofficer numbers.
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/7
