FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1779584596
OL,3,CPolice bill for investigation into SNP
OL,4,Cfinances tops #2m
OL,6,F"The chief constable has already
OL,7,Fclearly stated the financial situation
OL,8,Ffacing the force, with a significant
OL,9,Fshortfall in funding.
OL,11,F"The incoming Justice Secretary Neil
OL,12,FGray must heed this warning before it
OL,13,Fis too late."
OL,15,FShe urged Ivan McKee, who was this
OL,16,Fweek appointed to the new role of
OL,17,FPublic Service Reform Secretary, to
OL,18,Fexplain whether his job will require
OL,19,Fhim to make "brutal cuts" to public
OL,20,Fservices and whether this would
OL,21,Finclude Police Scotland.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@AOUuD@MO]{D@MOU{D@YO]
