OL,3,CPolice bill for investigation into SNP
OL,4,Cfinances tops #2m
OL,6,FA spokesperson for the Scottish
OL,7,FGovernment said: "We are providing
OL,8,Frecord funding of over #1.7 billion
OL,9,Ffor policing in 2026-27, a 5% increase
OL,10,Fcompared to 2025-26.
OL,26,@oD@ROU
