OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1779584596
OL,3,CPolice bill for investigation into SNP
OL,4,Cfinances tops #2m
OL,6,F"Scotland continues to have more
OL,7,Fofficers per capita than England and
OL,8,FWales and the Chief Constable recently
OL,9,Fconfirmed at the Criminal Justice
OL,10,FCommittee that the budget allocation
OL,11,Fwill allow her to prioritise front-
OL,12,Fline services for our communities and
OL,13,Fto ensure that she can maintain
OL,14,Fofficer numbers at 16,500 in the
OL,15,Fcoming year. Allocation of resources
OL,16,Fis a matter for the Chief Constable."
